description: Small Planked Texas Walnut is a red brown and charcoal design. The beauty is showcased within the small planks made up of light and dark variations. The design can be paired with Y0466K-12 Planked Texas Walnut.

name: Small Planked CA Walnut
description: Small Planked California Walnut is dark brown with charcoal graining that can be paired with Y0465K-12 Planked California Walnut. The beautiful colorations of deep brown and chocolates make this design perfectly on trend.

name: Tawney  Marquetry
description: Tawney Marquetry is a warm mid-tone brown wood that is a large scale pieced marquetry pattern. This coordinates with Tawney Line.

name: Tawney Line
description: Tawney Line is a warm mid-tone brown wood that is straight grained. Black graining is running throughout the pattern.

name: Tweedish Indigo
description: Tweedish Indigo is a deep blue indigo on indigo tweed pattern that has been abstracted.

name: Tweedish Pewter
description: Tweedish Pewter a grey on grey abstracted tweed textile pattern.

name: Silvermist
description: Silvermist is a beautiful warm white abstract pattern that looks like a solid, in an abstracted grid pattern.

name: Hematite
description: Hematite is a grey color that is similar to its stone namesake. This is an abstract pattern that gives the illusion of a solid in an organic grid pattern.

name: Night
description: Night is an abstracted organic grid pattern in a charcoal grey optical solid.

name: Twilight
description: Twilight is a light dusky blue optical solid pattern. The pattern is made up of a small organic grid.

name: Stockholm Mod
description: Stockholm Mod Y0577 is a large scale graphic wood paired with overlapping whites and greys. Available in a casual rustic finish giving a Scandinavian feeling.

name: Lush Bermuda
description: Lush Bermuda is a large tropical botanical in muted blues, greens, and greys. The background is made up of a muted pink textile look, the color is inspired by the pink beaches in Bermuda.

name: Vintage Chevron
description: Vintage chevron is a large scale distressed silver colored pattern. This design radiates nostalgic glamour.

name: Sable Marquetry
description: Sable Marquetry is a coordinated marquetry pattern to Sable Line. The Large scale pieced pattern is a taupe with black straight grain.

name: Sable Line
description: Sable Line is a linear woodgrain in taupe with black grain running throughout.

name: Mocha Olive
description: Mocha Olive is a large scale dark brown monochromatic wood design in a unique figured pattern.

name: Cement
description: Cement Grey is a solid mid-tone cool grey color.

name: Battleship
description: Battleship is a cool steel grey abstract in a soft crossweave pattern offering overall color and up-close interest.

name: Mushroom
description: Mushroom is a heathered grey crossweave pattern of rich overall color and detailed interest.

name: Magnolia
description: Magnolia is a white neutral abstract in a soft crossweave pattern offering overall color and extraordinary dimension.

name: Morris Oak
description: Morris Oak is a plain sliced classic oak design in a refined ebony color and impressive embossed and aligned texture.

name: Carter Oak
description: Carter Oak is a handsome, weathered oak design in shades of warm grey enhanced by an embossed and aligned texture.

name: Stickley Oak
description: Stickley Oak is a deep coffee color oak design reinforced by an authentic embossed and aligned texture, reminiscent of the Prairie style.

name: Fisher Oak
description: Fisher Oak is a classic aged oak design with detailed graining and features that highlight the embossed and aligned texture.

name: Ruskin Oak
description: Ruskin Oak is a beautiful example of an all-American oak design. The light honey color and rich, warm undertones showcase the authentic embossed and aligned texture.

name: Ashbee Oak
description: Ashbee Oak is a quiet and reserved oak design of light taupe and mocha graining that accentuates the woodgrain of the embossed and aligned texture.

name: Java  Mahogany
description: Java Mahogany is a beautiful wood in a deep coffee brown hue which is full of delicate graining and cross firing. This medium scale Mahogany is a  vulnerable species from Central America.

name: Indigo Kilim
description: Indigo Kilim is a beautiful medium scale design inspired by Kilim rugs. This pattern is given a modern feel with monochromatic indigo blues and a time worn look.

name: Baltic Blue Ikat
description: Baltic Blue Ikat is a stunning cobalt blue large scale cheveron pattern. This design was inspired by the Ikat weaveing tradition.

name: Fog Ikat
description: Fog Ikat is a large scale warm mid-tone grey pattern. This chevron pattern is  inspired by Ikats from Central Asia.

name: Shadow Ikat
description: Shadow Ikat is a dark charcoal large scale chevron pattern in a woven Ikat stye.

name: Tarnished Kilim
description: Tarnished Kilim is a dark monochromatic steel grey is a modern interpretation of the Kilim rug. This medium scaled allover pattern has a time worn look, adding visual interest.

name: Raw Eucalyptus
description: Raw Eucalyptus is a large scale design in a natural coloration. It features golden tones with warm grey and dark brown graining.

name: Umber Makore
description: Umber Makore is an endangered wood from West Africa.  This medium sized straight grained wood is a midtone warm brown with subtle cross firing throughout.

name: Natural Zebrawood
description: Natural Zebrawood features bold ebony straight graining in a medium scale design. West African zebrawood is a vulnerable species.

name: Quartered Koa
description: Quartered Koa, an elegant straight grain wood from Hawaii, has a rich amber -red coloring. The woodgrain is full of beautiful flaming, common to Koa.

name: Fawn Eucalyptus
description: Fawn Eucalyptus is a warm café au lait coloration with deep gold and brown graining running throughout the large scale wood.

name: Sienna Eucalyptus
description: Sienna Eucalyptus is a large scale dark warm brown wood with charcoal graining running thorughout.

name: Autumn Mahogany
description: Autumn Mahogany is a medium sized wood in rich golden brown with subtle planking. This vulnerable species features cross firing.

name: Midnight Ebony
description: Midnight Ebony is a bold large scale woodgrain in rich browns and black. The wood is full featured with unique cathedrals and contrasting light brown graining.

name: Indonesian Rosewood
description: Indonesian Rosewood is a beautiful fawn brown exotic wood. Full cathedrals in deep brown are found throughout this stunning large scale woodgrain.

name: Heartwood Cocobolo
description: Heartwood Cocobolo is an exotic wood in a deep rich brown. Black graining and pale sap lines are found throughout the large scale woodgrain.

name: Carbon Cloth
description: Carbon Cloth is a graphite grey woven pattern.

name: Oxidized Diamond Plate
description: Oxidized Diamond Plate  is a charcoal design with a diamond plate pattern.

name: Zinc Diamond Plate
description: Zinc Diamond Plate is a medium grey design with a diamond plate pattern.

name: Silver Diamond Plate
description: Silver Diamond Plate is a pale silver design with a diamond plate pattern.

name: Asian Amber
description: A vertical grain bamboo laminate design in tones of amber-orange.

name: Cottage Ash
description: Cottage Ash is a dramatic ash with full and partial cathedrals. The woodgrain is a mid-tone brown with warm lighter brown color play throughout.

name: Chocolate Ash
description: Chocolate Ash is an ash that is a rich deep brown. The graining looks like it was charred with midtone browns highlighted  through the wood grain, creates a dramatic deep woodgrain.

name: Tide Pool
description: Tide Pool is a soft blue with overlapping patterning that creates a texture.

name: Denim
description: Denim is a textural overlapping pattern in the color of blue denim.

name: Piedra Flor
description: Piedra Flor is a distressed charcoal colored design with a dimensional overlapping circle pattern repeating throughout.
